            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour</strong> and <strong>Marmite</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong></p><p>Add 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong> gradually and stir well (this is to ensure there's no lumps!) – this is your <strong>gravy mix</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>shredded spring greens</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
